additionalDomainsTabGuidance: Bakisa ba domaines personnalisés mpo na kokotisa na catégorie moko na moko. Ba sources oyo ewutaka na ba domaines wana ekozala marqué na icône ya catégorie oyo ekokani. Tyá domaine moko na ligne moko na format 'example.com'.
additionalStringsTabGuidance: Bakisa ba modèles ya URL personnalisé mpo na kokotisa na catégorie moko na moko. Ba sources oyo ezali na ba modèles ya URL oyo ekozala na elembo ya catégorie oyo ekokani. Tyá motindo moko na molɔngɔ moko (ndakisa, '/search?q=', '/article/', '?page=nsango').
additionalUrlStrings: Ba nsinga mosusu ya URL (moko na molongo)
categoriesTabGuidance: Activer to désactiver ba catégories spécifiques ya ba citations. Ba catégories désactivées ekolakisa ba icônes te to ekobima na tableau de bord te.
categoryHints.advocacy: Source oyo ezali organisation ya défense.
categoryHints.blacklisted: Source oyo etiemaki na liste noire mpo na abuse persistant, typiquement na forme ya ba liens externes ya spam.
categoryHints.blogs: Source oyo ezali poste ya blog.
categoryHints.books: Eutelo oyo ezali mokanda lokola buku, zulunalo, to mikanda misusu.
categoryHints.community: Liziba oyo ezali nsango ya mboka.
categoryHints.deprecated: Liziba oyo ezali lisusu na ntina te mpe esengeli kosalelama te. Ekoki kaka kosalelama mpo na kolobela makambo oyo bato bazali na yango to makambo oyo bato ya mayele babimisaka bango moko.
categoryHints.editable: Liziba oyo ekoki kobongisama na lisanga (ndakisa, wiki to base de données).
categoryHints.generallyReliable: Ba rédacteurs bandimaka mingi que source oyo ezali fiable na ba sujets na domaine ya expertise na yango.
categoryHints.generallyUnreliable: Mingimingi, liziba oyo etalelami lokola oyo ekoki kotyelama motema te na bato ya mboka. Ekoki naino kosalelama mpo na komilobela oyo ezali na ntembe te to makambo oyo bato ya mayele bamibimisi.
categoryHints.government: Liziba oyo emonisami lokola bopanzi sango ya leta to ya leta, to liziba ya leta.
categoryHints.marginallyReliable: Liziba oyo ezali mwa kotyela motema. Ekoki kozala na ntina kotalela yango na kotalela likambo mokomoko mpo na koyeba soki ekoki kotyelama motema na likambo mokomoko.
categoryHints.multi: Boyokani ezali te na kati ya lisanga mpo na bondimi ya source oyo. Bondimi na yango ekoki kozala na bopusi na likambo moko to mingi, lokola esika ya lisolo, mokomi, to ntango ya kobimisa mikanda.
categoryHints.news: Eutelo oyo ezali lisolo ya bansango ya ebongiseli moko ya bansango oyo eyebani mingi.
categoryHints.opinions: Source oyo ezali pièce ya opinion.
categoryHints.predatory: Liziba oyo euti na zulunalo moko oyo elyaka banyama mosusu.
categoryHints.press: Source oyo ezali communiqué ya presse.
categoryHints.satire: Eutelo oyo ebimisaka makambo ya satirique to ya parody.
categoryHints.social: Eutelo oyo ezali site ya social media, mbala mosusu poste ya social media.
categoryHints.sponsored: Source oyo ezali contenus sponsorisé to matériel promotionnel.
categoryHints.tabloids: Source oyo eza tabloïde to sango ya bilobaloba.
categoryHints.tvPrograms: Liziba oyo ezali programme ya TV to ya radio. Bondimi na yango etali programme ya moto na moto.
categoryLabels.marginallyReliable: oyo ekoki kotyelama motema na ndenge ya moke

suggestionsDialogGuidance: Pona catégorie moko to ebele pona citation oyo pe na option pesa commentaire. Onglet ya sika ekofungwama na formulaire ya bobongisi oyo etondisami liboso na Meta Wiki esika okoki kotinda likanisi na yo mpo na botali.
suggestionsDialogReliabilityGuidance: Mpo na biteni ya bondimi (oyo ezali na liste ya moindo, oyo esili kosalelama te, oyo ezali mingimingi ya kotyela motema, oyo ezali mingimingi ya kotyela motema te, oyo ezali na bondimi moke, boyokani te), tosengi yo oluka libaku ya kozwa boyokani na moko ya nkasa ya mosala oyo elandi. Ba catégories ya bondimi ezongisami na mikolo na tango na kotalaka boyokani ya baimboka oyo ekomami na nkasa oyo.
